dc_title_s: Plat book of Antrim Co., Mich.
dc_description_s: Extent: 1 atlas (18 unnumbered pages) | Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners. | Notes: Publication date estimated by designation of M-31 and M-131 being state (not federal highways) and M-32 going no further west than Elmira.|Scale determined from section lines. | Scale approximately 1:51,000
